    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "+sj8O8S8htUFl94k2dwQDhO4a0Qn5qxZdwfqDbNtW1w=",
    "originContent": "### 2. With manual recompilation",
    "translatedContent": "### 2. 手动重新编译方式"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "Tg8gVC84vmCX5Wc5sA3jqEOz9nA+DGK4rZ2roJsIBMY=",
    "originContent": "You can use `typst-live` to reload pdf files without recompilation of source files.",
    "translatedContent": "你可以使用 `typst-live` 来在不重新编译源文件的情况下重新加载 pdf 文件。"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "9cZaEIhvlC8pLR0bg85/VsWka2/icVaw/F9F+uvQVNM=",
    "originContent": "For that you want to use `--no-recompile` option which disables recompilation and just hosts",
    "translatedContent": "为此，你需要使用 `--no-recompile` 选项，该选项禁用重新编译，仅在浏览器标签页中托管"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "92j1DBarg2p3ay1YCLp9PuRg281n4IISxmtan9rKjgY=",
    "originContent": "your pdf file in browser tab, you will need to specify `filename` as pdf instead of source `.typ` file.",
    "translatedContent": "你的 pdf 文件，你需要指定的 `filename` 为 pdf 文件而非源 `.typ` 文件。"
